SERVER CREATION
---------------

BASIC COMMANDS

1) Creating package.json --- npm init
2) Install express --- npm i express
3) Install JWT --- npm i jsonwebtoken
4)Install mongoose---npm i mongoose   //to connect mongodb with db.js
  

BASIC STEPS

1) Create a folder
2) Create package.json
3) Install express
4) Create index.json
5) Import Express inside the index.js
6) Create app using express
7) Setup port number
8) Resolving http methods
9) HTTP response code
   1xx-information
   2xx-Success
   3xx-redirection
   4xx-client error
   5xx-server error
10)JWT (JSON web token) -fpr authentication
   jwt.sign()
11)Middleware 
   1.Application specific Middleware   
12)Database Integration   
   Using mongoose
   Database connection
   
    